{"prompt": "Generate a website for a podcasting network. The website should be professional and use blue as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Podwave Network</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #2c3e50; /* Dark Blue */\n            --secondary-color: #34495e; /* Slightly Lighter Blue */\n            --accent-color: #ecf0f1; /* Light Gray */\n            --text-color: #ffffff;\n            --hover-color: #1abc9c; /* A subtle teal for hovers */\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            border-bottom: 5px solid var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.8em;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n\n        nav {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 15px 0;\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        nav a {\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 15px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            transition: color var(--hover-color) ease-in-out;\n        }\n\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: var(--hover-color);\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 20px auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n\n        #hero {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 60px 0;\n            background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--primary-color), var(--secondary-color));\n        }\n\n        #hero h2 {\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        #hero p {\n            font-size: 1.3em;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: var(--hover-color);\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: background-color ease-in-out 0.3s;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: var(--accent-color);\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        .content-section {\n            padding: 40px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        .content-section h3 {\n            font-size: 2em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        .podcast-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));\n            gap: 25px;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n        }\n\n        .podcast-item {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            padding: 20px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            text-align: left;\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease-in-out, box-shadow 0.3s ease-in-out;\n        }\n\n        .podcast-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-10px);\n            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);\n        }\n\n        .podcast-item img {\n            max-width: 100%;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n        }\n\n        .podcast-item h4 {\n            font-size: 1.4em;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        .podcast-item p {\n            font-size: 0.95em;\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n            opacity: 0.9;\n        }\n\n        .podcast-item a {\n            color: var(--hover-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-weight: bold;\n        }\n\n        .podcast-item a:hover {\n            text-decoration: underline;\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px 0;\n            margin-top: 40px;\n            border-top: 5px solid var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n\n        footer a {\n            color: var(--hover-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <h1>Podwave Network</h1>\n        <p>Your Source for Engaging Audio Content</p>\n    </header>\n\n    <nav>\n        <a href=\"#about\">About Us</a>\n        <a href=\"#podcasts\">Our Podcasts</a>\n        <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n    </nav>\n\n    <section id=\"hero\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Discover Your Next Favorite Podcast</h2>\n            <p>From insightful interviews to captivating stories, we bring you the best in audio entertainment.</p>\n            <a href=\"#podcasts\" class=\"cta-button\">Explore Our Shows</a>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"about\" class=\"content-section\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h3>About Podwave Network</h3>\n            <p>Podwave Network is dedicated to creating and distributing high-quality podcasts that inform, entertain, and inspire. We partner with passionate creators to deliver diverse voices and compelling narratives to listeners worldwide.</p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"podcasts\" class=\"content-section\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h3>Featured Podcasts</h3>\n            <div class=\"podcast-grid\">\n                <div class=\"podcast-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/250x150/34495e/ffffff?text=Podcast+Art+1\" alt=\"Podcast 1\">\n                    <h4>The Innovation Hub</h4>\n                    <p>Exploring the cutting edge of technology and its impact on our lives.</p>\n                    <a href=\"#\">Listen Now</a>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"podcast-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/250x150/34495e/ffffff?text=Podcast+Art+2\" alt=\"Podcast 2\">\n                    <h4>History Uncovered</h4>\n                    <p>Delving into forgotten stories and pivotal moments that shaped our world.</p>\n                    <a href=\"#\">Listen Now</a>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"podcast-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/250x150/34495e/ffffff?text=Podcast+Art+3\" alt=\"Podcast 3\">\n                    <h4>Mindful Living</h4>\n                    <p>Practical advice and inspiration for a balanced and fulfilling life.</p>\n                    <a href=\"#\">Listen Now</a>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"podcast-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/250x150/34495e/ffffff?text=Podcast+Art+4\" alt=\"Podcast 4\">\n                    <h4>The Creative Spark</h4>\n                    <p>Interviews with artists, writers, and creators about their journey.</p>\n                    <a href=\"#\">Listen Now</a>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"contact\" class=\"content-section\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h3>Get In Touch</h3>\n            <p>Have a podcast idea or want to collaborate? We'd love to hear from you.</p>\n            <p>Email: <a href=\"mailto:info@podwave.net\">info@podwave.net</a></p>\n            <p>Follow us on social media!</p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Podwave Network. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}